ion is derived from subsec. (g) of former ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s264"},"text":"section 264 of this title","children":[],"tail":". See Codification note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1811"},"text":"section 1811 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"iddc647d7b-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2006—Par. (5). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/173"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–173","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Deposit Insurance Fund” for “Bank Insurance Fund or the Savings Association Insurance Fund”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/171"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–171","children":[],"tail":" repealed "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/208/s2704/d/14/F"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–208, § 2704(d)(14)(F)","children":[],"tail":". See 1996 Amendment note below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1996—Par. (5). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/208/s2704/d/14/F"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–208, § 2704(d)(14)(F)","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “Deposit Insurance Fund” for “Bank Insurance Fund or the Savings Association Insurance Fund”, was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/171"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–171","children":[],"tail":". See Effective Date of 1996 Amendment note below and 2006 Amendment note above."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1989—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/73"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–73","children":[],"tail":" amended section generally. Prior to amendment, section read as follows: “The factors to be enumerated in the certificate required under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1814